Élodie Fontan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89lodie_Fontan 0 Élodie Fontan (born 9 July 1987) is a French actress. She has appeared in more than fifteen television and film productions since 1996. Élodie_Fontan ( born 9_July_1987 ) is a_French_actress .
